headline: Equity Residential: Q2 Earnings Snapshot
summary: CHICAGO (AP) — Equity Residential (EQR) on Monday reported a key measure of profitability in its second quarter. The results met Wall Street expectations. The Chicago-based real estate investment trust said it had funds from operations of $386.8 million, or 99 cents per share, in the period.
